song_name: Mary Ellen Makes The Moment Count

version_description: The strumming patterns I chose are just something to start with and to get the idea. Intro and verse 1 can also be picked.
This version is 99% true to the original studio version. The only doubt I have is about the passage at the end of the verse progression but I think A/C# fits well.
Kinda off jazzy and some crazy chords , but you can have a lot of fun playing this.
This tab is based off the version of Take On Me that plays in Deadpool 2 ( https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xohx2jFLF8Y ).
